{"tid":1074789,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 Apple 將推出真無線 Beats Powerbeats 運動耳筒","createTime":"2019-03-23T15:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T01:14:57.000Z","uid":25260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6e461e966092faa8f350dd81ddd7c7d4037e05","tid":1074789,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:50:54.000Z","msg":"Apple 最近推出第二代 AirPods 之後，其使用的 H1 晶片看來很快會在 Beats 耳筒中應用。最近有消息指 Apple 將會推出真無線版本的 Beats Powerbeats 耳筒，針對運動耳筒市場。<br />\n<br />\nPowerbeats 耳筒是 Beats 旗下的運動耳筒產品，主打比較牢固的佩戴設計，而消息指新推出的 Powerbeats 耳筒將會採用真無線設計，左右耳筒會完全分開，並搭載新的 H1 無線晶片，帶來更大的自由度，相信基本功能會與 AirPods 類似，並支援「喂 Siri」功能。<br />\n<br />\n據稱這新耳筒將在下月推出，對比起 AirPods，Powerbeats 將會有更強勁的低音，也會提供防水功能，方便運動時佩戴聽歌。不過，消息並沒有提及售價方面的詳情。而 Beats 其他耳筒產品會否同時推出更新加入 H1 晶片，則仍然有待進一步的公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2019/03/22/apple-wire-free-powerbeats-april/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2019%2F03%2F22%2Fapple-wire-free-powerbeats-april%2F&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEGDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=36b7d2cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.macrumors.com/2019/03/22/apple-wire-free-powerbeats-april/</a><br />\n<br />\nH1 + in-ear = 無敵 ？"},{"pid":"31e51ea9f454c96e9bf3d549d1c284667812f1f8","tid":1074789,"uid":209225,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"有消息指<br />\n看來<br />\n據稱<br />\n相信<br />\n有待進一步的公佈"},{"pid":"e21dc1389a92643ca79eb329bad42599c08c12db","tid":1074789,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e51ea9f454c96e9bf3d549d1c284667812f1f8","tid":1074789,"uid":209225,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"有消息指<br />\n看來<br />\n據稱<br />\n相信<br />\n有待進一步的公佈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"傳"},{"pid":"4898d8ea3f9c293ac6677af6a4ed9f48c662f9a4","tid":1074789,"uid":124577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"